PRODUCTION READY RELEASE v1.0.0

This is the first stable release of JQBSTM32 Framework, ready for use in
production environments. All components have been thoroughly tested and
documented. The API is now stabilized with backward compatibility guaranteed
within the 1.x version series.

This framework includes implementations based on publicly available standards
and specifications. See the ACKNOWLEDGMENTS file for detailed information
about the standards and specifications used.

For complete source code, documentation, and examples, visit:
https://github.com/JAQUBA/JQBSTM32_Framework

Release Information:
- Version: 1.0.0
- Release Date: December 8, 2024
- License: LGPL-3.0-or-later
- Files: 65 source files with LGPL headers
- Examples: 15+ complete examples
- Documentation: Complete API reference

